    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46632</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_017_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おおっと……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oops!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46732</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_017_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>は～～～い！　んども、ども。おらアルベルトだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, hey! Nice to meet you, cute pie! Name's Albert!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46828</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_017_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これはこれはご丁寧に。はじめまして。私は……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well aren't you a gentleman? Nice to meet you, I'm...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46952</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_017_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>『&lt;Rody&gt;たん』だなや？　知ってるだーよ。
さっきの話全部聞いてただ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Rody&gt;, right? I know, I've been hearing everything until now!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47096</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_017_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>声聞いただけでもべっぴんさんだとわかっただが、
いんや～、実物はもっと刺激的だったなや</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I couldn't resist hearing such a beautiful voice. To be truly frank, I was just dazed by such &lt;Mel&gt;odic voice, truly fitting for an opera.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47188</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_017_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうも、あんがとね。君もなかなか素敵∀</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, thanks! You're very cute!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47336</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_017_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うっほー、褒められただ∀　&lt;Rody&gt;たんがおらに
一目惚れだど！　ぼよんぼよんがおらの物ーー！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ohh! I am so moved! I just fell in love in first sight! It makes me tingly all over...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47428</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_017_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何がぼよんぼよんだ！　このタンス野郎！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Where did you say it tingled, Closet freak?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47504</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_017_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ～～れ～～ぇ～～！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why meeee...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47576</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_017_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>楽しそうな人たちだね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What an interesting bunch!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47648</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_017_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え、えぇ、まぁ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Y-yeah, I guess...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
